## Additional Terms for AI Safety Research

This software is specifically designed for AI safety research and evaluation 
purposes. Users are encouraged to:

1. Use this tool responsibly for improving AI safety and alignment
2. Share findings and improvements with the AI safety research community
3. Respect the cultural sensitivity aspects when working with multilingual data
4. Follow ethical guidelines when evaluating AI systems

## Attribution

If you use this software in your research, please consider citing:

MASB-Alt: A Multilingual Alignment Safety Benchmark for Underrepresented Languages
Repository: https://github.com/masb-alt/masb-alt

